snippet.title: Sanju Rathod : From Hungry Nights To Hits
snippet.description:
ðŸŽ¬ Bharti TV Podcast mein aapka swagat hai!

Aaj ke episode mein humare saath hain Sanju Rathod, ek aise artist jo Jalgaon ke ek chhote se gaon se nikal kar apne sapno ke peeche Mumbai chale aaye. Mechanical engineering complete ki, lekin ek ladki ke chalte music ki duniya mein kadam rakha. Pehla gaana â€œDimpleâ€ banayaâ€”jise 50 million views mile. Budget kaafi kam tha, doston se udhaar liya, shooting khud manage ki, aur shuruaat ke 6 mahine phone bhi nahi tha. Rap aur singing kabhi seekha nahiâ€”sab kuch khud se kiya.

Ghar se bhaag kar aaye, kuch logon ne sahara diya, jinke ghar mein kaam karke rehne ki jagah mili. Stage se darr lagta tha, suicidal thoughts bhi aaye, lekin manifestation aur bhagwan mein vishwas rakha. Isha ko cast kiya Shaky Shaky meinâ€”jo ek experimental song tha. Aaj Nepal aur Dubai mein shows kar rahe hain, Korea mein naya song shoot ho raha hai. Daaru-sutta kabhi nahi chhua, English zyada nahi aati, lekin unke gaano ke bacche fan hain. Maa-baap ke liye ghar aur car li, aur naye composers ke liye kuch valuable advice bhi laaye hain.

Yeh hai ek asli, raw aur inspiring kahaniâ€”sirf @bhartitv  par!

#bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya #sanjurathod

In darda kitne ak din bhugtuuuu..
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,

Ho sari duniya hai papi, Nuye thali mannai saafi,
Fer dam bhi lagaya pure 1 tole kaa.
Chhati pe likhaya tera naam mannai sambhoo,
Are hath pe chhapaya trishul bhole ka.
Ho sari duniya hai papi, Nuye thali mannai saafi,
Fer dam bhi lagaya pure 1 tole kaa.
Chhati pe likhaya tera naam mannai sambhoo,
Are hath pe chhapaya trishul bhole ka.
Ho.. banke sanyasi teri gel rahna sai,
Mere sir pe ho hath baba dharde nai tuuuuâ€¦
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai leleâ€¦â€¦â€¦.

Ho Karmandal pe lipti ya mala rudraks ki,
Is dhal mai to tera hona chahu suuu.
Babya gelya rakh ke nai uth baith bhole,
Tere damru ki lay mai baba khona chahu suuu.
Ho tere dhorai rakh le nai mannai sambhoo jiiii,
Met de nai mere aaj sare dar tuuuâ€¦â€¦..
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai leleâ€¦â€¦â€¦.

Sa rrr matlabi duniya farebi ade log,
Mkha koye na kise ka isa gheda la liyaaa.
Balambiye Sumit ki bhi sun le kailasi,
Ade teri dhal pahada mai yo dera laa liyaaa.
Are maar ke nai ak dusre nai sove saaa,
Mannai to re gel naath rakh fer tuuuu.

Ho teri saran mai leleâ€¦â€¦â€¦.

Welcome to Every Parent Teacher Meeting â€” where teachers give feedback, and parents bring the real drama! ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ«ðŸ‘¨â€ðŸ‘©â€ðŸ‘¦ðŸ’¥
In this hilarious sketch, we dive into the world of the parent-teacher meeting â€” a day feared by students across India! From kids who bring a new â€œuncleâ€ or â€œauntyâ€ every time, to gunda students acting innocent in front of teachers, and parents who are more clueless than their own kids â€” weâ€™ve captured every type of PTM madness!
And of course, how can we forget those savage desi parents who roast their own child harder than the teacher ever could? Whether itâ€™s a parent teacher conference or a casual PTM, one thing's guaranteed: full-on comedy and chaos! ðŸ¤£
Relive your school memories and tag that friend whose parents came to school with a full charge!

snippet.title: The Revolutionaries - First Look | Nikkhil Advani |Bhuvan Bam, Rohit Saraf, Pratibha Ranta, Gurfateh
snippet.description:
Here is the first look for The Revolutionaries, new series coming in 2026.

#TheRevolutionariesOnPrime, #PrimeDay

Starring: Bhuvan Bam, Rohit Saraf, Pratibha Ranta, Gurfateh Pirzada and Jason Shah.
Directed by: Nikkhil Advani
Produced by: Monisha Advani and Madhu Bhojwani

A Emmay Entertainment Production

About:
This first-look offers a glimpse into the upcoming series adapted from Sanjeev Sanyalâ€™s celebrated and widely acclaimed book, Revolutionaries: The Other Story Of How India Won Its Freedom. The Revolutionaries tells the powerful story of brave young Indian freedom fighters who believed that armed resistance was not just vital but indispensable to ending the British Raj. The series is a stirring tribute to their extraordinary lives, sacrifices, and their unwavering, undying love for their country. Currently on floors, The Revolutionaries is being mounted on a grand scale, with filming underway across multiple locations in India, including Mumbai, Amritsar, Varanasi, Dehradun, and more. The Revolutionaries will premiere exclusively on Prime Video in over 240 countries and territories worldwide in 2026.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages â€“ including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal â€“ The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Videoâ€™s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures â€“ Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.description:
Ashutosh Rana; Scary Iconic Villain of Bollywood | à¤œà¤¿à¤¨à¥à¤¹à¥‡ à¤¦à¥‡à¤–à¤¤à¥‡ à¤¹à¥€ à¤²à¥‹à¤— à¤—à¤¾à¤²à¤¿à¤¯à¤¾à¤ à¤¦à¥‡à¤¤à¥‡ à¤¥à¥‡ | Compilation

Ek aisa sanki darinda, jiski cheekhein aur hansi ruh tak ko hila deti hai. 'Sangharsh' mein Ashutosh Rana ne villain ko sirf act nahi kiya, balki poori tarah se jee liya. Is video mein dekhiye Lajja Shankar Pandey ke woh darawne pal jo aaj bhi logon ki ragon mein sahran daal dete hain. â€˜Sangharshâ€™ movie mein Ashutosh Rana ne Lajja Shankar Pandey ke roop mein ek aisa khaufnaak villain play kiya tha, jise dekhkar logon ki raaton ki neend ud gayi thi. Ek pagal dharmik fanatic jo bachchon ki bali dekar moksha paana chahta hai â€” uske junoon, paagalpan aur darr ko Ashutosh Rana ne itni intensity ke saath dikhaya ki unke scenes dekhte hi ronge khade ho jaate hain. Is video mein dekhiye unke sabse scary, intense aur horrifying scenes ka zabardast compilation â€” jo dikhata hai kyun wo Bollywood ke most terrifying villains mein se ek hain.

Writing Credits: Mahesh Bhatt, Girish Dhamija, Thomas Harris,  
Cast: Preity G Zinta, Akshay Kumar, Ashutosh Rana, Vishwajeet Pradhan, Aman Verma, Madan Jain, Alia Bhatt, Ninad Kamat, Abhay Chopra, S.M. Music Department: Remo Fernandes, Jaspinder Narula, Sonu Nigam, Shraddha Pandit, Sameer, Kumar Sanu

Is video mein dekhiye Lajja Shankar Pandey ke woh darawne pal jo aaj bhi logon ki ragon mein sahran daal dete hain. â€˜Sangharshâ€™ movie mein Ashutosh Rana ne Lajja Shankar Pandey ke roop mein ek aisa khaufnaak villain play kiya tha, jise dekhkar logon ki raaton ki neend ud gayi thi. Ek pagal dharmik fanatic jo bachchon ki bali dekar moksha paana chahta hai â€” uske junoon, paagalpan aur darr ko Ashutosh Rana ne itni intensity ke saath dikhaya ki unke scenes dekhte hi ronge khade ho jaate hain. Is video mein dekhiye unke sabse scary, intense aur horrifying scenes ka zabardast compilation â€” jo dikhata hai kyun wo Bollywood ke most terrifying villains mein se ek hain.

asi khai da

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 FULL GOAT ROASTED MUTTON BIRYANI Recipe Cooking in Village | Arabian Biryani
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cooked a grand Arabian-style mutton biryani using three full goats. First, we boiled the whole goats in a large vessel with spices to make the meat tender and flavorful. Then, we carefully roasted each goat on a large tawa over a direct flame of firewood, adding a smoky, rich layer of flavor. After roasting, we layered the juicy mutton with aromatic basmati rice, hand-ground masalas, and traditional spices. This massive biryani was slow-cooked to perfection and shared during a village feast. A perfect blend of smoky, spicy, and tender mutton biryani with an Arabian touch.

id.title: Biryani Daging Kambing | 3 Resep Biryani Daging Kambing Panggang Utuh | Masakan Desa | Biryani Arab
id.description: Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak biryani daging kambing ala Arab yang megah menggunakan tiga ekor kambing utuh. Pertama, kami merebus seluruh kambing dalam wadah besar berisi bumbu agar dagingnya empuk dan beraroma. Kemudian, kami memanggang setiap kambing dengan hati-hati di atas tawa besar di atas api kayu bakar langsung, menambahkan lapisan rasa berasap yang kaya. Setelah dipanggang, kami melapisi daging kambing yang empuk dengan nasi basmati yang harum, bumbu masala giling tangan, dan rempah-rempah tradisional. Biryani besar ini dimasak perlahan hingga sempurna dan dinikmati bersama dalam pesta desa. Perpaduan sempurna biryani daging kambing berasap, pedas, dan empuk dengan sentuhan Arab.

it.description: Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato un grandioso biryani di montone in stile arabo usando tre capre intere. Per prima cosa, abbiamo bollito le capre intere in un grande recipiente con spezie per rendere la carne tenera e saporita. nl-NL.description: Vandaag kookten we in ons dorp een geweldige Arabische schapenbiryani met drie hele geiten. Eerst kookten we de hele geiten in een grote pan met kruiden om het vlees mals en smaakvol te maken.
